item.title: XGN68-12-indoor-AC-box-type-metal-enclosed-switchgear
item.description: The switchgear is a 3.6, 7.2, 12KV three-phase AC 50Hz single-bus section indoor complete device for receiving and distributing electric energy. It also has the functions of controlling, protecting and monitoring circuits, and can be used in various types of power plants, substations, industrial and mining enterprises, high-rise buildings, etc., and can also be combined with ring main units in switching stations.
